transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, this is Vagrant.

Speaker 2: Yes, this is Tommy Longhorn.

Speaker 1: You all have been sending me prescriptions,

Speaker 2: and I'm not able to take these prescriptions,

Speaker 1: so I'm having to send some back,

Speaker 2: but I need to stop you from sending any more.

Speaker 1: May I have your phone number linked to the prescription

Speaker 2: so I can locate you?

Speaker 1: 972-768-8082.

Speaker 2: Oh, yeah, Mr. Tommy Longhorn.

Speaker 1: Okay, yeah, so you were saying that you cannot take that anymore.

Speaker 2: You want to pause it and reorder yourself?

Speaker 1: Well, no, I want to cancel any further orders

Speaker 2: because I'm sending these back because I can't take it.

Speaker 1: Okay, just write refuse return on it,

Speaker 2: and you can return it, and I'll cancel your account, okay?

Speaker 1: Okay, I'll get in the mail tomorrow, I tell you.

Speaker 2: I'm sorry?

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: You're welcome.

Speaker 1: Uh-huh.
